entries.quest_escort_d: A full wing of blackscale elite pilots will be escorting the blackscale leader to Kashyyyk.
entries.quest_escort_t: A group of blackscale elite pilots are flying escort for Blackscale leader
entries.quest_location_d: A new blackscale leader is heading for the Planets surface. He must not be allowed to land.

entries.title: Space Kashyyyk: Fall of the Black Scale
entries.title_d: A new blackscale leader and his escort have arrived in Kashyyyk. Wipe them out and leave no survivors.
